I finally managed to include the font file. Using custom_rules.xml seems to be the proper way to accomplish this but I didn&#39;t have any luck with that approach. Instead I put the assets folder in the Packaging project folder and added three lines to the file ***(Solution_name).Packaging.androidproj***

    &lt;ItemGroup&gt;
      &lt;Content Include=&quot;assets\LiberationSans-Bold.ttf&quot; /&gt;
    &lt;/ItemGroup&gt;

Then the font file content was included in the .apk and could be accessed with Asset Manager as described in my previous post.

